A '''sonic pacifier''' was a modular device capable of emitting vibrational waves of force that could affect the inner [[Ear/Legends|ear]] of any organism caught within its radius. The weapons merchant, [[Orion Ferret]], owned such a device and used it to control a creature known as a [[Watchbeast]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]], [[Patch-4]]. In [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]], [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] used Ferret's sonic pacifier to render the Watchbeast known as [[Ceasar]] unconscious.

